				<td colspan="2"><span>Delegate MA would help more in pulling then mark npc imho.  If you set the MA as the tank of your group you will clearly see what he has targeted.  So even if you dont see adds when you pull anything that doesnt have the pretty MA ring on it you know to mez/charm.
